{"tid":1011153,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"今曰初二，已經同老婆因拜年問題吵大鑊","createTime":"2019-02-06T14:07:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T14:48:08.000Z","uid":52127,"like":23,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"82839a05e234f06e902f45a9248edb03f6462f92","tid":1011153,"uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:07:58.000Z","msg":"好唔開心，點解過年都唔俾我開心一兩日？係都要令我咁難受...<br />\n<br />\n實情是這樣，我上年樓市高峰時上車，買了間港島東的窩居，兩百幾呎，開放式套房，已傾注我所有儲蓄，還要月供接近兩萬蚊，已經好辛苦。<br />\n<br />\n今個農曆新年，是我倆口子第一個新年，老婆約了兩班親友上來拜年，我已經同佢講過間屋太細，不便招呼客人，其實上茶樓飲茶見面已可。但老婆不聽，還是照約無誤。。<br />\n<br />\n昨天還可以，她親友還算客氣，雖然有幾位沒有位子坐，但我有心已好難受。。<br />\n<br />\n到今早，她的大學同學，出事了。。<br />\n<br />\n我老婆是港島某名牌大學畢業，她的同學嫁的都是專業人仕，所住的地方都不會是我這類型窩居，問題來了，她們一行八人上來，有大人細路，不夠位子座已經知道，心諗，快點派完利是送客好了，但，有兩位小友說肚餓，老婆就煎了底年糕，一落鑊，全間屋都是油煙味，我心想，今次大鑊了。。<img src=\"https://finance.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default/smile_22.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.discuss.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fsmile_22.gif&h=ccd803d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無意中，我看到她其中一個同窗手機whatsapp跟群組訴說，邊有人住咁細既屋，仲要煎塊糕都搞到全屋油煙味。。<br />\n<br />\n我借意話要落樓下買氣水，忍受不住，哭了。。<img src=\"https://finance.discuss.com.hk/images/smilies/default/cry.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.discuss.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fsmilies%2Fdefault%2Fcry.gif&h=686b3705&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9da66afa155a833ea8d1ff6c945f9bc3b5252d17","tid":1011153,"uid":223063,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"堅持堅持 幾多錢一茶匙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509b8c13ed5dc471d19db74985101a5be79528c9","tid":1011153,"uid":130774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:14:10.000Z","msg":"辛苦你啦 bro"},{"pid":"cbaab41a634c28201095edce57a8298564dbfef6","tid":1011153,"uid":125261,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:15:13.000Z","msg":"抄鄉土既<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=28018951&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D28018951%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYAexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=494f426c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=28018951&amp;extra=page%3D1</a>"},{"pid":"cf5efb4b2b382a58b2c355fd50f71937eeaab51b","tid":1011153,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:16:35.000Z","msg":"冇錢就唔好買港島樓啦"},{"pid":"259b5f2bcbf8177dcebdec7c258b01c013c9955e","tid":1011153,"uid":41524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:34:04.000Z","msg":"too long no see<br />\n離婚唔洗講咁多<br />\n男人老狗咪成舊垃圾咁"},{"pid":"6b36389d66e0b604867def49a60eb198aba51bfe","tid":1011153,"uid":117947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"老實講真係有啲細"},{"pid":"7742a1170de641544eb218a26bd1d589dc9a21bc","tid":1011153,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:39:16.000Z","msg":"兩百幾就算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2a2253fcc2b32b0b8ef70de305118aa85842dff","tid":1011153,"uid":72734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71831b7fdedef249a0c4045e825b35669fc90d5c","tid":1011153,"uid":132486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T17:23:58.000Z","msg":"做男人做到咁廢，真係好咩？"},{"pid":"0f17a8d5687277e2ce4a9c7cbac1630a6f5c6496","tid":1011153,"uid":87389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T17:28:54.000Z","msg":"又bin c"},{"pid":"a